      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "See #b#p602##k in #m10005000# to awaken the #b#t1302009##k."
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I showed #p602# #p502#'s #b#t1302009##k, and he claimed to have made it himself. He said he needs #b1 #t4020109#, 1 #t4003004#, 1 #t4001007#, and 1 #t4001008##k to awaken it. Unfortunately, I've never heard of any of those items... He recommended talking to #r#p513# in #m10004121##k to find them."
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I gathered the materials needed for the awakening and took them to #p602#. #p602# used the materials to reawaken the #t1302009# into the #b#t1302014##k. It's a nice sword radiating a mysterious light... It's a shame I have to give it to #p502#."
    },
