      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "So you want to reawaken this sword. It's not an easy task, though. Not only will you need to gather up hard-to-find materials, you'll also need a rare scroll for it. But if you still want to go along with it... Then I want you to gather up the materials I'm about to tell you. I don't know if you can do it, but..."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Bring me 1 #b#t4020109##k, 1 #b#t4003004##k, 1 #b#t4001007##k, and 1 #b#t4001008##k… I'm not sure how you should get these... #p513# in #m10004121# might know something..."
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "My goodness! You did collect #b1 #t4020109##k, #b1 #t4003004##k, #b1 #t4001007##k, and #b1 #t4001008##k! Alright, then."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Hold on one second. I haven't done this in ages, but... with these materials, I may be able to pull off the magic and reawaken the #b#t1302009##k."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirName": "2",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Incredible... Tristan's sword... I didn't think I'd live to see this again. "
      },
